# reply-hook commands are used to exec config commands based on recipients of the
# message, see https://neomutt.org/guide/configuration.html#reply-hook
# note it's matched against the message you are replying _to_, instead of the message
# you are _sending_; send-hook is matched against all messages, both new & replies.
